{
 "name": "RPlog_It_s_Lorn_Rhys",
 "title": "It's Lorn Rhys",
 "summary": "In the lounge of an Imperial space station (OSG), the smuggler Morganna Tazecks arrives under guard to deliver luxury goods, only to be intercepted by Moff Lorn Rhys. A seasoned interrogator, Lorn probes her about how a civilian gained access to the station's restricted areas and her connection to its commander, Captain Atrox. Morganna grows increasingly flustered and evasive, alternately defiant and forcibly polite as Lorn presses her and threatens detention by COMPNOR. Unsatisfied and amused by her reluctance, Lorn announces he will raise the matter with Captain Atrox before coolly exiting the lounge.",
